What's the right course of action?  I wish I knew 100%.  But I'm not a political science major and I really don't keep up with politics as well as some others here.  You can only make a truly right decision with 100% information and knowledge, which will never be possible.  I guess it's called trial and error.  If we find a massive increase in terror attacks after doing this, then maybe we should back off and see what happens.  I happen to think a situation like the one we're in can only be solved via trial and error =/.<br>
